raw: * The tangible theme is inspired by ideas from material design. A lot of work went into designing a higly automated color
* system. In order to customize the theme to your taste, simply create your own color system. Use qx.theme.tangible.ColorLight for inspiration.
* The Tangible Theme is very new and still in a state of flux. PRs highly welcome. Use https://material.io as a visual guide.

@description.body: Tangible Theme (Light) The tangible theme is inspired by ideas from material design. A lot of work went into designing a higly automated color system. In order to customize the theme to your taste, simply create your own color system. Use qx.theme.tangible.ColorLight for inspiration. The Tangible Theme is very new and still in a state of flux. PRs highly welcome. Use https://material.io as a visual guide.
